tool.description:
Purpose:
Updates incident records with AI-recommended service, service offering, and configuration item (CI) values. It also adds work notes summarizing all field changes and recommendations

Input Parameters:
- incidentNumber (required): The incident number to update
- recommendedService (optional): JSON string or object with format {sysId: <string>, name: <string>}
- recommendedOffering (optional): JSON string or object with format {sysId: <string>, name: <string>}
- recommendedCI (optional): JSON string or object with format {sysId: <string>, name: <string>}

Returns:
- status: "success" or "error"
- message: Descriptive message about the update result or error details
